title: Nemesis (Hands On Misty & Daeron 2010 ReMasterMix)
info: This is a remastered version of my Hands On "1" remix of Misty & Daeron's wonderful mod Nemesis. This time out i did some EQ'ing on the tracks to get a MOAR crisp sound. This is the first track out from the remastered version of Hands On to be re-released, hopfully, in beginning of 2011.
